description: Try our easy to follow Chicken & Avocado Rice Paper Rolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken & Avocado Rice Paper Rolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Using rice paper wrappers, soak one at a time in warm water for 30 seconds and then place on a damp tea towel. Place an 1/8 ingredients into each wrap and roll tightly. Repeat and serve rolls with salt-reduced soy sauce.
